 log_distance_market_town, log_distoxroad, log_dist_hmb, log_dist_cph 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
Constant or no constant? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Looks like no constant in Berger 2019 eq 1, however does this make sence?
 In my understanding including a constant in the simple regression: 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta Y_{p}=\theta_{0}+\alpha_{c}$
\end_inset

, the interpretation of the constant would be the average change in the
 outcome variable of the ommited county (ie.
 
\begin_inset Formula $E(\Delta Y_{p}\vert\alpha_{c}=0)$
\end_inset

).
 
\end_layout

